{
  "message": "test(polynomial): lock Laguerre and Legendre arithmetic parity\n\nAdded 13 fixtures across Laguerre (lag*) and Legendre (leg*) basis\nops, each of which had a single fixture. Completes the classical\northogonal polynomial arithmetic coverage started with Chebyshev\nand Hermite.\n\nLaguerre (L_n):\n- lagadd: equal-length, short+long padding\n- lagsub: long-minus-short tail\n- lagmul: scalar\u00d7vector, (L0+L1)\u00b2 via the -n L_n + (2n+1) L_n - ...\n  recurrence \u2192 [2.0, 0.0, 2.0]\n- lagdiv: textbook quotient [2.54167, 1.91667, 0.66667] /\n  remainder [-5.375]\n- lagval: L_2 at [0, 1, 2] \u2192 [1.0, -0.5, -1.0] (Laguerre L_2(x)\n  = (x\u00b2-4x+2)/2)\n\nLegendre (P_n):\n- legadd: short+long padding\n- legsub: long-minus-short tail\n- legmul: (P0+P1)\u00b2 = 4/3 + 2x + 2x\u00b2/3 via (2n+1) L_n recurrence\n- legdiv: quotient [-0.208, -0.25, 3.333] / remainder [1.375]\n- legval: P_2 at \u00b11, 0 \u2192 [1.0, -0.5, 1.0] (nodes of Gauss-Legendre\n  order-2), full series at 0.5 \u2192 0.875\n\n159 polynomial_differential cases total (from 146).\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
